<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
        "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
    <title>访问出错啦</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 40px;
            line-height: 500%;
            color: #F00;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 26px;
            line-height: 350%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px 0;
            width: 800px;
            border: 1px solid #CCC;
            background-color: #F7F7F7;
        }

        .content span {
            line-height: 250%;
            font-size: 26px
        }

        .content li {
            line-height: 250%;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="title">404 提示：您访问的页面出错啦！</div>
<div class="content">
    <span>请尝试以下操作：</span><br/>
    <li style="text-align: left;padding-left: 100px;">确保浏览器的地址栏中显示的网站地址的拼写和格式正确无误。</li>
    <li style="text-align: left;padding-left: 100px;">如果通过单击链接而到达了该网页，请与网站管理员联系，通知他们该链接不正确。</li>
</div>
</body>
</html>
<script type="text/javascript">
    window.setTimeout(function () {
        var domain = window.location.host;
        window.location.href = 'http://' + domain + '/';
    }, 3000);
</script>
